item.description:
@Blue-Jy was kind of going for older sound but I can’t figure out the modulations needed to produce staticky or airy stuff so I usually always go with high amounts of reverb which sounds cool but is ultimately my backup plan and not my original idea

Thank you for listening

item.title: Lunar Legends - Insomniac [House?]
item.dc:creator: anon86704580
item.description:
Very pretty dude! Strain feels a bit… out of place, although the strings fit nicely. Drums arr pretty cool! Gotta love the string section. Drop felt a bit disappointing at 1:44 All in all, for a new Auxy artist, awesome track!

Versatility: 8/10
Creativity: 8/10
Predictability: 6/10
Use of Instruments/Automation: 6/10
Feeling: 9/10

Overall: 37/50
